                     <interp inst="t18470705-1611-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp> for stealing 2 gowns, value 16<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 1 petticoat, 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; the good of <persName id="t18470705-name-338" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18470705-name-338" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
